### Liste des publications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/publications
Accept: application/json

### Création publication (échoue si job inexistant)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/publications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Développeur Java",
  "description": "Nous recherchons un développeur Java expérimenté",
  "numberOfPositions": 2,
  "status": "Open",
  "jobId": 999999
}

### Création publication (modifier jobId avec un ID existant)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/publications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ingénieur QA",
  "description": "Automatisation des tests",
  "numberOfPositions": 1,
  "status": "Open",
  "jobId": 1
}

### Détail publication
GET http://localhost:8080/api/publications/1
Accept: application/json

### Suppression publication
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/publications/1

